text: Jamie Maclaren (born 29 July 1993) is an Australian soccer player. He plays for Melbourne City in the A-League Men and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:Soccer players from Melbourne Category:2018 FIFA World Cup players Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players
